<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 15:11:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>分析师预计稀土价格将在 2024 年下半年反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rare-earths-prices-seen-rebounding-second-half-2024-analysts-2024-02-05/</link><description>分析师表示，稀土价格可能已经触底，并有望在今年晚些时候上涨，因为电动汽车和风电的需求以及主要生产国中国预计将取消扩大的产量配额。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:55:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rare-earths-prices-seen-rebounding-second-half-2024-analysts-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>工作忧虑让中国人回家度假心情不好</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/job-worries-sour-mood-chinese-heading-home-holidays-2024-02-05/</link><description>周一，中国工人们挤上火车回家过农历新年假期，他们对工作和经济不景气的担忧给人们期待已久的家庭团聚蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:31:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/job-worries-sour-mood-chinese-heading-home-holidays-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>杨恒均：这句话对中澳关系意味着什么</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-harsh-sentence-australian-writer-tests-limits-rebound-ties-2024-02-05/</link><description>分析人士表示，澳大利亚作家杨恒均周一在北京被判处死刑缓期执行，这不太可能破坏澳中关系，但将考验堪培拉在多年紧张关系后推动两国关系重回正轨的努力的极限。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:24:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-harsh-sentence-australian-writer-tests-limits-rebound-ties-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：随着股市暴跌，中国券商限制跨境互换--消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-brokers-restrict-cross-border-swaps-stocks-plunge-sources-2024-02-05/</link><description>据六位知情人士透露，为了捍卫疲软的股市，包括国有巨头中国国际金融公司（中金公司）在内的中国券商限制了国内投资者可以进行的跨境掉期交易金额。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-brokers-restrict-cross-border-swaps-stocks-plunge-sources-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚人杨恒均在中国被判处死刑缓期执行，他是一位富有魅力的博主、间谍小说家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/yang-hengjun-australian-given-suspended-death-sentence-china-was-charismatic-2024-02-05/</link><description>澳大利亚博主杨恒均周一在北京一家法院出庭，因间谍罪名被判处死刑缓期执行，他在悉尼的朋友说，他看起来“非常瘦弱，非常脆弱”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/yang-hengjun-australian-given-suspended-death-sentence-china-was-charismatic-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>雅诗兰黛因中国经济复苏延迟而裁员；股价飙升16%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/estee-lauder-slashes-annual-profit-forecast-cut-jobs-2024-02-05/</link><description>化妆品巨头雅诗兰黛周一表示，将在全球裁员约 3% 至 5%，以扩大其利润率，因为其中国业务的复苏需要比预期更长的时间。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 11:49:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/estee-lauder-slashes-annual-profit-forecast-cut-jobs-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国法案对药明康德及其西方制药商合作伙伴构成风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-bill-poses-risk-wuxi-apptec-its-western-drugmaker-partners-2024-02-05/</link><description>公开数据显示，美国一项法案草案引发了中国生物技术公司药明康德股票的抛售，这不仅对该公司造成重大打击，还可能影响许多依赖该公司进行研究和制造的实验室和西方制药商。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 11:09:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-bill-poses-risk-wuxi-apptec-its-western-drugmaker-partners-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>晨竞：狂风确实吹动了五月的娇嫩花蕾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-05/</link><description>Alun John 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 11:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>为什么以 52 亿美元出售俄罗斯 Yandex 意义重大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/why-52-bln-sale-russias-yandex-is-significant-2024-02-05/</link><description>经过数月的谈判后，周一宣布了一项价值 52 亿美元的现金加股票交易，将科技集团 Yandex（通常被称为“俄罗斯的谷歌”）的俄罗斯关键资产出售给俄罗斯投资者财团。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 10:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/why-52-bln-sale-russias-yandex-is-significant-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：AI芯片需求迫使华为放缓智能手机生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ai-chip-demand-forces-huawei-slow-smartphone-production-sources-2024-02-05/</link><description>对华为人工智能芯片的需求飙升，加上制造限制，迫使这家中国科技巨头优先考虑人工智能，并放慢了其高端 Mate 60 手机的生产速度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/ai-chip-demand-forces-huawei-slow-smartphone-production-sources-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>杨恒均：在中国什么是死刑缓期执行？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/what-is-chinas-suspended-death-sentence-verdict-2024-02-05/</link><description>澳大利亚作家兼民主博主杨恒均周一被北京一家法院判处死刑缓期执行，人权倡导者称，这是对间谍相关案件的异常严厉的判决。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:49:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/what-is-chinas-suspended-death-sentence-verdict-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告九架中国军机穿越海峡中线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-nine-chinese-military-aircraft-crossing-straits-median-line-2024-02-05/</link><description>台湾国防部周一表示，发现九架中国军机穿越台湾海峡敏感的中线，并与中国军舰进行“联合战备巡逻”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:23:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-nine-chinese-military-aircraft-crossing-straits-median-line-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国国家队无法拯救不断恶化的市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/why-chinas-national-team-wont-save-spiralling-markets-2024-02-05/</link><description>国家支持的买盘可能连续第二天将中国股市从多年低点拉升。投资者怀疑这种支持能否持续，并警告称这会导致市场失衡和不稳定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:21:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/why-chinas-national-team-wont-save-spiralling-markets-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾抵御来自中国黑客的网络攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-wards-off-cyber-attacks-china-based-hackers-2024-02-05/</link><description>一名信息和通信部官员周一表示，在中国活动的黑客试图闯入菲律宾总统和政府机构的网站和电子邮件系统，其中一个目的是促进海上安全，但失败了。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 07:36:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-wards-off-cyber-attacks-china-based-hackers-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>由于全球需求疲弱，德国12月出口令人失望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-fall-more-than-expected-december-2024-02-05/</link><description>德国联邦统计局周一公布的数据显示，由于全球需求疲软，德国12月份出口降幅超出预期，凸显了人们对欧洲最大经济体健康状况可能重新陷入衰退的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 07:19:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-fall-more-than-expected-december-2024-02-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>